The paper also discusses the use of low-dimensional factorization and classification, which are topics that are relevant to machine learning (ML) and could fall under the cs.LG (Machine Learning) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of embeddings for classification tasks, which is a topic that could fall under the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of embeddings in computer vision (CV) tasks, which could fall under the cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the use of embeddings in information retrieval (IR) tasks, which could fall under the cs.IR (Information Retrieval) sub-category.
